OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1778335888
OL,3,CCar 'driving at Jewish schoolboys'
OL,4,Ctreated as religiously aggravated
OL,5,Cassault
OL,7,FA car reportedly driving towards three
OL,8,FJewish schoolboys in north-west London
OL,9,Fis being investigated as a religiously
OL,10,Faggravated assault.
OL,12,FThe vehicle was reported to have
OL,13,Fmounted the kerb where the 14-year-
OL,14,Folds were standing, the Metropolitan
OL,15,FPolice said.
OL,17,FThe children moved out of the way and
OL,18,Fno injuries were reported from the
OL,19,Fincident that took place at around
OL,20,F3.40pm in Holders Hill Road, Barnet,
OL,21,Fon April 20.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/6
