OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1778335888
OL,3,CCar 'driving at Jewish schoolboys'
OL,4,Ctreated as religiously aggravated
OL,5,Cassault
OL,7,FThe father of one of the boys told the
OL,8,FBBC that there were dozens of children
OL,9,Fin kippot (skullcaps) nearby and his
OL,10,Fson was left "shaken, but with it".
OL,12,FHe said: "They were visibly Jewish
OL,13,Fkids. He was waiting at the lights and
OL,14,Fsaw these kids and saw an opportunity."
OL,16,FThe headteacher of Hasmonean High
OL,17,FSchool for Boys sent a letter to
OL,18,Fparents on the police appeal for
OL,19,Fwitnesses, according to the BBC.
OL,21,FNo arrests have been made.
OL,26,@rD@NOUrD@bO]tD@JOUvD@gO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/6
