OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1778335888
OL,3,CCar 'driving at Jewish schoolboys'
OL,4,Ctreated as religiously aggravated
OL,5,Cassault
OL,7,FA Met spokesperson said: "While
OL,8,Finquiries are ongoing to establish the
OL,9,Fcircumstances, this is currently being
OL,10,Ftreated as a religiously aggravated
OL,11,Fassault.
OL,13,F"We remain in close contact with the
OL,14,Fnearby school."
OL,16,FOn Wednesday the force announced a
OL,17,Fcommunity protection team of 100 extra
OL,18,Fofficers to help safeguard the Jewish
OL,19,Fcommunity.
OL,26,@oD@ZOUuD@AOUvD@OO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/6
