OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1778335888
OL,3,CCar 'driving at Jewish schoolboys'
OL,4,Ctreated as religiously aggravated
OL,5,Cassault
OL,7,FIt said in its initial phase, the new
OL,8,Fteam will be "primarily focused on
OL,9,Fprotecting the Jewish community, which
OL,10,Ffaces some of the highest levels of
OL,11,Fhate crime alongside significant
OL,12,Fterrorist and hostile state threats".
OL,14,FIt added that it would bring together
OL,15,F"neighbourhood policing, specialist
OL,16,Fprotection and counter terrorism
OL,17,Fcapabilities" to provide a "more
OL,18,Fvisible, intelligenceled and co-
OL,19,Fordinated presence focused on
OL,20,Fprotecting Jewish communities across
OL,21,FLondon".
OL,26,@pD@NOUtD@dO]wD@AOUyD@MO]yD@\OU}D@GO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/6
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
