OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1778335888
OL,3,CCar 'driving at Jewish schoolboys'
OL,4,Ctreated as religiously aggravated
OL,5,Cassault
OL,7,FMetropolitan Police Commissioner Sir
OL,8,FMark Rowley previously said 300 more
OL,9,Fofficers were needed to tackle the
OL,10,Frise in antisemitism across the
OL,11,Fcapital.
OL,13,FJewish charity the Community Security
OL,14,FTrust (CST) said: "The incident was
OL,15,Freported to CST and is being
OL,16,Finvestigated by the police and we urge
OL,17,Fanyone who witnessed this to contact
OL,18,Fthe police and CST."
OL,26,@vD@SOUzD@TO]
